name: [LoRA] Senko-san | Multiple outfits
description:
An attempt at a anime-styled Senko-san model.

Trained with Kohya's scripts, has miko, swimsuit, sleepwear (currently brokey) and maid outfits.

Multiplier range of 0.6-0.9 seems to work the best, set to 1.0 to get the anime artstyle.

Trigger words:

  • senko-san miko

  • senko-san swimsuit

  • senko-san sleepwear

  • senko-san maid
